criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  own a smart phone;

          -  18 years or above;

          -  sufficient language skills (completed secondary school education);

          -  carry a singleton fetus;

          -  at a gestational age of 28 to 30 weeks;

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  have existing medical conditions or pregnancy complications which may inhibit
             breastfeeding initiation, according to their medical doctor;

          -  intend to give birth in health institutes other than the study hospitals.
